message: >-
  If you use this software in research, please cite it as below. This file makes the
  project citable-as-a-work (GitHub, Zenodo, and reference managers read it directly);
  the `licenses` gate keeps its `version` and `license` in lockstep with package.json,
  so a release can never ship a citation that points at the wrong version.
